                <strong>üì± Breakpoints:</strong><br>
                ‚Ä¢ <code>col-</code> = Extra small (&lt;576px)<br>
                ‚Ä¢ <code>col-sm-</code> = Small (‚â•576px)<br>
                ‚Ä¢ <code>col-md-</code> = Medium (‚â•768px)<br>
                ‚Ä¢ <code>col-lg-</code> = Large (‚â•992px)<br>
                ‚Ä¢ <code>col-xl-</code> = Extra large (‚â•1200px)
            </div>
